---
alwaysApply: true
---

When working with authenticated domain data (profile, orders, subscriptions, settings, etc):

- Never fetch initial data on the client using useSWR or useEffect
- Never store auth tokens in client state managers
- Always fetch authenticated data in a Server Layout or Server Component
- Hydrate SWR cache using fallback
- Use SWR only for mutations and background sync

Follow /docs/authenticated-data-fetching.md
